NAME:
   enaptercli.test provisioning standalone - Create a new standalone device

USAGE:
   enaptercli.test provisioning standalone [command options]

OPTIONS:
   --verbose                      log extra details about operation (default: false)
   --site-id value, -s value      site ID where to craate device
   --device-name value, -n value  name for a new device
   --help, -h                     show help

ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES:
   ENAPTER3_API_TOKEN  Enapter API access token
   ENAPTER3_API_HOST   Enapter API base URL (https://api.enapter.com by default)

